STATE of Connecticut
v.
Denis HICKEY. Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided June 21, 2016.

Katharine Goodbody, assigned counsel, New Haven, in support of the petition.

Nancy L. Chupak, senior assistant state's attorney, in opposition.

The defendant's petition for certification for appeal from the Appellate Court, 165 Conn.App. 901, 136 A.3d 681 (2016), is denied.
